What you need to know:

United went out to Pep Guardiola's men in the final four of the competition last season, before losing in the semis of the FA Cup and Europa LeagueUnited have pushed on again this season in the league to find themselves level on points with Liverpool at the top of the table with a game in hand on the champions.United have not won a trophy since last lifting the League Cup and Europa League in Jose Mourinho's first season in charge, four years ago